### 9. Create Billing Page (`Components/Pages/Billing.razor`)

A page to create invoices, process payments, and view payment history:

```razor
@page "/billing"
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization
@using VetClinic.Data
@using VetClinic.Services
@attribute [Authorize]
@inject ClinicService Clinic

<PageTitle>Billing</PageTitle>

<h1>Billing</h1>

<ul class="nav nav-tabs mb-3">
