### 8. Create Appointments Page (`Components/Pages/Appointments.razor`)

A page with a weekly calendar view showing time slots, ability to create/reschedule/cancel appointments, and real-time availability checking.

```razor
@page "/appointments"
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization
@using VetClinic.Data
